bio: Swipe right if you’re ready to laugh your way through life! I'm Aryan, a 28-year-old Mumbai explorer, stand-up comedy enthusiast, and aspiring photographer. I’m the type who’ll hit the gym with you at dawn and chase sunsets across the globe by dusk. Empathy is my superpower, and I’m here for both the deep conversations and the spontaneous dance-offs in the living room. Looking for someone who can handle sarcasm as well as they handle sincerity. Let’s create memories that are as vibrant as our city! 🌅😄
